TITLE: HTML Structure for Simple Box Widget in CKEditor 5
DESCRIPTION: This HTML snippet demonstrates the structure of a Simple Box widget in CKEditor 5. It includes the necessary CSS styles and an example of the widget's HTML structure in the editor content.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ckeditor/ckeditor5/blob/master/docs/tutorials/widgets/implementing-a-block-widget.md#2025-04-16_snippet_5

