					<p>The description goes here.</p>
					<ul>
						<li>It can contain lists,</li>
						<li>and other block elements like headings.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>

		<script src="dist/bundle.js"></script>
	</body>
</html>
```

