LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
editor.conversion
	.for( 'upcast' )
	.attributeToAttribute( {
		view: {
			key: 'class',
			value: /styled-[\S]+/
		},
		model: {
			key: 'styled'
			value: viewElement => {
				const regexp = /styled-([\S]+)/;
				const match = viewElement.getAttribute( 'class' ).match( regexp );

				return match[ 1 ];
			}
		}
	} );
```

