TITLE: Implementing Converter Definitions in CKEditor 5 Plugin
DESCRIPTION: Defines downcast converter for transforming model abbreviation attributes into HTML elements in the view. Uses attributeToElement() helper to convert between model and view representations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ckeditor/ckeditor5/blob/master/tests/manual/abbreviation-level-3.md#2025-04-16_snippet_6

