TITLE: Handling User Input in Form View
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of form submission handling to insert abbreviation with user-provided values.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ckeditor/ckeditor5/blob/master/tests/manual/abbreviation-level-2.md#2025-04-16_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
class AbbreviationUI extends Plugin {
	_createFormView() {
		const editor = this.editor;
		const formView = new FormView( editor.locale );

		this.listenTo( formView, 'submit', () => {
			const title = formView.titleInputView.fieldView.element.value;
			const abbr = formView.abbrInputView.fieldView.element.value;

			editor.model.change( writer => {
				editor.model.insertContent(
					writer.createText( abbr, { abbreviation: title } )
				);
			} );

		} );

		return formView;
	}
}
```

