TITLE: Defining Keyboard Navigation Testing Steps for To-Do List in RTL Context
DESCRIPTION: Markdown checklist detailing the process for testing keyboard navigation in a to-do list with right-to-left content, focusing on arrow key usage and navigation behavior.
