DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how changes to observable properties are automatically reflected in the DOM. It renders a `Button` view, and then changes its `label`, `isOn`, and `isEnabled` properties, showing how the corresponding DOM element is updated accordingly due to the property bindings defined in the template.
