TITLE: Transforming Non-Semantic Oembed Elements with Iframely - HTML
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet handles <div data-oembed-url> elements, removing any static previews first and then loading the actual media preview through Iframely.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ckeditor/ckeditor5/blob/master/packages/ckeditor5-media-embed/docs/features/media-embed.md#2025-04-16_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: html
CODE:
```
<script>
	document.querySelectorAll( 'div[data-oembed-url]' ).forEach( element => {
		// Discard the static media preview from the database (empty the <div data-oembed-url="...").
		while ( element.firstChild ) {
			element.removeChild( element.firstChild );
		}

		// Generate the media preview using Iframely.
		iframely.load( element, element.dataset.oembedUrl ) ;
	} );
</script>
```

