TITLE: Configuring ESLint for CKEditor 5 in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines the ESLint configuration for the CKEditor 5 project. It extends the 'ckeditor5' configuration and sets specific rules for the project, including environment settings and overrides for certain file patterns.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ckeditor/ckeditor5/blob/master/packages/ckeditor5-list/tests/manual/todo-documentlist-rtl.md#2025-04-16_snippet_1

