TITLE: Implementing SimpleBoxEditing Plugin with Schema Definition
DESCRIPTION: Creates the editing component of the SimpleBox plugin and defines the schema for the simple box, title, and description elements.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ckeditor/ckeditor5/blob/master/docs/tutorials/widgets/implementing-a-block-widget.md#2025-04-16_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
import { Plugin } from 'ckeditor5';

export default class SimpleBoxEditing extends Plugin {
	init() {
		console.log( 'SimpleBoxEditing#init() got called' );

		this._defineSchema();
	}

	_defineSchema() {
		const schema = this.editor.model.schema;

		schema.register( 'simpleBox', {
			inheritAllFrom: '$blockObject'
		} );

		schema.register( 'simpleBoxTitle', {
			isLimit: true,
			allowIn: 'simpleBox',
			allowContentOf: '$block'
		} );

		schema.register( 'simpleBoxDescription', {
			isLimit: true,
			allowIn: 'simpleBox',
			allowContentOf: '$root'
		} );
	}
}
```

