TITLE: Configuring Webpack for CSS Extraction
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript snippet demonstrates how to configure Webpack to extract CKEditor 5 CSS into a separate file. It uses mini-css-extract-plugin and sets up the necessary loaders and plugins.
