TITLE: Converting Block Image from Editing to Data View in CKEditor 5
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates the conversion of a block image from editing view to data view in CKEditor 5. It creates an img element and sets its attributes based on the model.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ckeditor/ckeditor5/blob/master/packages/ckeditor5-image/tests/manual/imageblock.md#2025-04-16_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
conversion.for( 'editingToData' ).elementToElement( {
    model: 'imageBlock',
    view: ( modelElement, { writer } ) => {
        const img = writer.createEmptyElement( 'img' );
        writer.setAttributes( {
            src: modelElement.getAttribute( 'src' ),
            alt: modelElement.getAttribute( 'alt' )
        }, img );
        return img;
    }
} );
```

