TITLE: Extending CKEditor 5 Schema for Text Highlighting
DESCRIPTION: This code extends the CKEditor 5 schema to allow a new 'highlight' attribute for text nodes. It's part of implementing text highlighting functionality.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ckeditor/ckeditor5/blob/master/docs/tutorials/crash-course/model-and-schema.md#2025-04-16_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
editor.model.schema.extend( '$text', {
	allowAttributes: 'highlight'
} );
```

